{"tid":925051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港係咪靜靜雞改左名叫香港市？","createTime":"2018-12-02T14:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T12:30:04.000Z","uid":175599,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6387b89733fe374d29c433316617dfb09225d8","tid":925051,"uid":175599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"近排幫人補習諗住download下啲past paper<br />\n發現考評局已經改左廣東話做廣州話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老尾你係咪叫深圳市考評局<br />\n乜撚野廣州話？<br />\n一係粵語<br />\n一係廣東話<br />\n幫人補習已經見到好多撚多普教中<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾考評局同化已經做到愈黎愈出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/02/221715_bd3f6906c5a054dacaf2194b58797e73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F02%2F221715_bd3f6906c5a054dacaf2194b58797e73.png&h=2e19990d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a51ce15a3a0111ce49ed8f7fc42018047f421253","tid":925051,"uid":43178,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"下，有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n我屌，又廣東又粵<br />\n咁支那嘅？叫香港話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f558c107ecde468fed459e01e149e4adaf31ea6c","tid":925051,"uid":26506,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"常用字廣州話讀音 <br />\n香港教育署語文教育學院中文系編 <br />\n1990年出版‧1992年修訂 <br />\n<br />\n幫人補習唔識就查下粵語、廣東話、廣州話、廣府話、白話呢啲字詞起源先啦，垃圾就出少句聲唔好教壞學生 得唔得"},{"pid":"26fe0dea726ad3c21894bf7b650e44970bfe57d7","tid":925051,"uid":175599,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"f558c107ecde468fed459e01e149e4adaf31ea6c","tid":925051,"uid":26506,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"常用字廣州話讀音 <br />\n香港教育署語文教育學院中文系編 <br />\n1990年出版‧1992年修訂 <br />\n<br />\n幫人補習唔識就查下粵語、廣東話、廣州話、廣府話、白話呢啲字詞起源先啦，垃圾就出少句聲唔好教壞學生 得唔得